vote.title: An ordinance granting a revocable license to HSV Leasehold, LP, for the use of a total of approximately 9,159 square feet of land to occupy, maintain and utilize three landscape and irrigation areas on portions of Mockingbird Lane and Hillside Drive rights-of-way near its intersection with Hillside Drive - Revenue: General Fund $200.00 one-time fee, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
